      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but at a much better price, you\u2019ve found it. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
