      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation interface, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It has been meticulously garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather or salt. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, reflecting the low-mileage, pampered life this car has led. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a collector-grade example that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new vehicle.",
